SubjectP.C. 2011-757 of June 23, 2011 ** AMENDMENT **
PrecisOrder amending the French version of Order in Council P.C. 2011-757 of June 23, 2011, in order to replace “9 699 hectares (23 957 acres)” by “9,699 hectares (23,957 acres)” for the setting apart of lands for the use and benefit of the LENNOX ISLAND BAND for a new reserve, identified as LENNOX ISLAND BAND INDIAN RESERVE No. 6, in Prince Edward Island.
